These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: sprite, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, iced-tea
Sport: rowing, skateboarding, surfing, baseball
1. Beverage:sprite is on the right of Sport:surfing##1
2. Sport:baseball is on the far left##1
3. Sport:surfing is between Sport:skateboarding and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
4. Beverage:iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:soy-milk is between Beverage:hot-chocolate and Beverage:sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea         | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk | sprite       |
| Sport      | baseball | rowing | surfing   | skateboarding |

