.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: dancing, cooking, baking, singing
Nationality: canadian, australian, pakistani, german
1. Nationality:german is between Hobby:baking and Nationality:australian##2
2. Hobby:singing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:pakistani is on the right of Nationality:canadian##1
4. Hobby:dancing is on the left of Nationality:canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | cooking | dancing | baking | singing |
| Nationality   | australian    | german   | canadian | pakistani       |

